Name: ArchiveOrganizationReference
Description: A reference to the organization or an individual acting as the archive.

Name: Item
Description: Describes individual items held or distributed by the archive in connection with a study, group of studies, or resource packages. What constitutes an item is determined by the archive.

Name: Collection
Description: Describes a collection of items held or distributed by the archive in connection with a study, group of studies, or resource packages. What constitutes an collection is determined by the archive.

Name: DefaultAccess
Description: Describes access to the archive in general. The restrictions noted at this level apply to all holdings of the archive unless overridden for specified collections or items.

Name: FundingInformation
Description: Describes funding information in relationship to the archive and its activities. This may be archive wide or related to specific collections or projects within the archive.

Name: Budget
Description: This describes the archive budget. It can be repeated for distinct budget activities such as budget periods, specific projects or types of activity.

Name: QualityStatementReference
Description: A reference to a Quality Statement regarding the activities and operation of the archive. These may include access or preservation appraisal assessments or certification.

Name: Coverage
Description: Documents the spatial, temporal, and/or topical coverage of the archive or division of an archive.
